Whereas, in March 1913, the founders of Delta Sigma Theta
			 Sorority, Inc. participated in the Women’s Suffrage March in the District of
			 Columbia, the sorority’s first public act;

Whereas Delta Sigma Theta Sorority, Inc. has more than 900
			 chapters in the United States, England, Japan, Germany, the Virgin Islands,
			 Bermuda, the Bahamas, and South Korea;
